Fig. 4p
). Likewise, L-NAME did not change vessel diastolic diameters (
Fig. 4q
). The intrinsic contraction rate and amplitude of lymphatic collecting vessels thus appears to be in part dependent on lymphatic endothelial cell caveolar functions.

